Minecraft systems


Item elevator:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u6gicMn5ips

Note:  	Top should have water source offset by 1 block, flowing towards and ending over a hopper.
The hopper should be offset by 2, and one block lower than the water.
The Hopper will feed the system, or a chest.


